description.narrative: Access to pre-school education services and teaching quality have been supported to ensure that over 120% of annual target (2,000 children) most disadvantaged children benefited from educational services in a healthy, inclusive and quality learning environment. More than targeted number of children benefited from ECD programme due to additional funds raised by UNICEF Mongolia to improve indoor air quality and to reduce risk of air pollution in the kindergartens. Teacher capacity in inclusive education, and community and parents understanding on child development and participation in school activities have been strengthened through continuous training and advocacy activities. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:03/02/2020
